RUN_THIS_CODE

Follow these exact steps to start the Swing Score web UI and related helpers.
Copy-paste each command into the terminal (zsh) while in the project root.

1) ACTIVATE THE VENV
   source .venv/bin/activate

2) INSTALL MINIMAL DEPENDENCIES (only if you haven't already)
   pip install flask plotly tabulate requests pandas

3) START THE FLASK DEV SERVER (web UI)
   python3 -m backend.app

Then open this URL in your browser:
  http://127.0.0.1:5000/

If anything fails, copy the terminal output and paste it here and I'll help debug.
